  "text": [
    "Focus on the shapes.",
    ", a curl,",
    ", a layer,",
    ", a heap.",
    ", a small cloud,",
    ", a fine day to fly.",
    ", the anvil, stay grounded.",
    ", rain, be careful,",
    "don\u2019t take off near",
    ",",
    "a shapeless layer",
    "of rain, hail, ice, or snow.",
    "Ice weighs on the blades of your propeller,",
    "weighs on the entering edge of your wings.",
    "Read a cloud,",
    "decode it,",
    "a dense, chilly mass",
    "can shift, flood with light.",
    "Watch for clouds closing under you,",
    "the sky opens in a breath,",
    "shuts in a heartbeat."
  ],
  "title": "Flying Lesson",
  "year": ""
